{"id":26180,"date":"2024-02-13T15:58:12","date_gmt":"2021-10-13T10:28:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=26180"},"modified":"2024-11-27T21:39:30","modified_gmt":"2024-11-27T16:09:30","slug":"small-bathroom-ideas-on-budget","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-budget\/","title":{"rendered":"Stunning And Thrifty: Low Budget Small Bathroom Ideas"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Give a stately spin to your bathroom on a budget now!<\/span><\/i> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Your bathroom is your private sanctuary. It gives you that much-needed luxury to relax even when you really don\u2019t have time for it! That&#8217;s the reason why many homeowners think that they must splurge a lot on designing their bathrooms even though they are small or medium-sized. But what if we tell you the budget small bathroom ideas exist and you can make the most of them! Small bathroom ideas on a budget India can be easily pulled off with a bit of planning and thinking. All you need is an innovative design and exciting decor ideas that you can execute even on a modest budget.<\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Based on your requirements, preference for decor, budget small bathroom ideas are aplenty. From accessories to basics like flooring, accents \u2014 choose them right in your budget and then see how your <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/small-bathroom-design-ideas\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">small bathroom<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> transforms into a plush oasis you can call all yours.<\/span> <span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We have helped hundreds of homeowners with budget small bathroom ideas, which we also designed. These are some of the best tips shared by our experts on small bathrooms. Check them out:<\/span><\/p>\r\n<h2>Choose Indie Tiles For A Vivid Look<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pops of colours and textures make small bathrooms look more vivid and pepped up! To follow this budget small bathroom decor idea, select textured or patterned tiles from a local artisan store around you to follow this budget small bathroom decor idea. Using this decor idea, you could lay them across your mirror wall and create an iconic focal point in your small bathroom. The best part is that it doesn\u2019t cost a bomb to do so!<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26186\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26186\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26186 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154346\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-india-with-indie-tiles.jpg\" alt=\"Small bathroom ideas on a budget in India with indie tiles make a small bathroom look more vivid\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154346\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-india-with-indie-tiles.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154346\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-india-with-indie-tiles-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154346\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-india-with-indie-tiles-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154346\/small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-india-with-indie-tiles-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26186\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Available on budget, patterned designer tiles give a beautiful twist to your bathrooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Experiment With Earthy Textures<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While granite and marble are usually preferred for bathrooms, they tend to be costly. Instead of doing that, choose earthy options like Kota stones or red stones to grant an earthy, warm vibe to your bathroom. This decor hack works particularly well for small bathrooms as it creates a statement wall accent or flooring and aids natural cooling.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26187\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26187\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26187 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154353\/very-small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-with-kota-stone.jpg\" alt=\"Kota stone flooring for very small bathroom ideas on a budget creates an earthy vibe to space\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154353\/very-small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-with-kota-stone.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154353\/very-small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-with-kota-stone-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154353\/very-small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-with-kota-stone-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154353\/very-small-bathroom-ideas-on-a-budget-with-kota-stone-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26187\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Go for Kota stone flooring and create a cosy, pretty bathroom on a budget<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Keep It Minimal For A Sophisticated Look<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bare minimum essentials paired with neat flooring, mirror and bath accessories let you create a simple yet sophisticated bathroom. You need nothing to put this small <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bathroom-interiors\/bathroom-decor-ideas\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">bathroom decor idea<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to use. Just plan well and choose earthy flooring options like grey tiles and light colour laminates that could pair with them. Together they would give a minimal yet mesmerising look on a budget to your bath space.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26184\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26184\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26184 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154334\/minimal-small-bathroom-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget.jpg\" alt=\"Small bathroom decorating ideas on a budget in minimal creates a sophisticated yet straightforward bathroom\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154334\/minimal-small-bathroom-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154334\/minimal-small-bathroom-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154334\/minimal-small-bathroom-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154334\/minimal-small-bathroom-decorating-ideas-on-a-budget-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26184\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Fix up accent lights and mirrors to make your bathroom look more airy and expansive<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to see your dream home before its built\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/28145609\/want-to-see-dream-home-before-its-build.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\r\n<h2>Place Planters In Your Small Bathroom<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Whether you have a green thumb or not, planters are one of the most economical bathroom decor accessories that you can use! Order some of the fresh air infusing planters, bonsai and root them in chic ceramic pots. Place them around your main mirror in the bathroom or by the sink or toilet shelf. They would make your bathroom look more organic and cosy.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26181\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26181\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26181 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154315\/budget-small-bathroom-decor-ideas-with-planters.jpg\" alt=\"Budget small bathroom decor ideas, place planters around the mirror or by the sink for an organic look\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154315\/budget-small-bathroom-decor-ideas-with-planters.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154315\/budget-small-bathroom-decor-ideas-with-planters-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154315\/budget-small-bathroom-decor-ideas-with-planters-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154315\/budget-small-bathroom-decor-ideas-with-planters-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26181\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Always under budget, greens and indie planters are great for bathrooms<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Read More <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/air-purifying-indoor-plants\/\"><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Air Purifying Indoor Plants<\/span><\/i><\/a><\/p>\r\n<h2>Play With Pastels For A Luxurious Look<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">One of the best decor hacks for small bathrooms is to choose pastel hues for them. Pick lighter palettes for tiles, bathroom mats, mirror light, laminates and other accessories. These pale hues not only make your bathroom look more luxurious but also showcase your taste as a homeowner.\u00a0 So, choose a thin mirror with soft lights for it and let its magic unravel.<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26185\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26185\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26185 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154340\/small-bathroom-design-ideas-on-a-budget-with-pastel-hues.jpg\" alt=\"Pastel hues for small bathroom design ideas on a budget create a luxurious look for a small bathroom\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154340\/small-bathroom-design-ideas-on-a-budget-with-pastel-hues.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154340\/small-bathroom-design-ideas-on-a-budget-with-pastel-hues-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154340\/small-bathroom-design-ideas-on-a-budget-with-pastel-hues-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154340\/small-bathroom-design-ideas-on-a-budget-with-pastel-hues-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26185\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Pinks, whites, greys and blues will make your small bathroom upbeat<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<h2>Turn It Modern With Natural Lighting<\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Natural light can work wonders for your bathroom, and you wouldn\u2019t need to spend an extra dime for doing so. Let a tiny window be a natural light source for your bathroom. Place little planters, fragrances and knickknacks around it. Make use of its frames and dents to hold the other essentials, and you would have an airy, vibrant bathroom that would look nothing like a small one!<\/span><\/p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_26183\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-26183\" style=\"width: 940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-26183 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154327\/budget-small-bathroom-ideas-with-tiny-window.jpg\" alt=\"Budget small bathroom ideas, a tiny window let natural lights and lends vibrant to space\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154327\/budget-small-bathroom-ideas-with-tiny-window.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154327\/budget-small-bathroom-ideas-with-tiny-window-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154327\/budget-small-bathroom-ideas-with-tiny-window-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/13154327\/budget-small-bathroom-ideas-with-tiny-window-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-26183\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Make your small bedroom modern \u2014 let all the natural light in<\/figcaption><\/figure>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Go ahead and get all creative with these budget small bedroom decor ideas.\u00a0 You do not need an extensive budget or a grand plan to decorate your small bathroom. These simple yet stately decor ideas will level up your small bathroom to nothing less than an upstate hotel\u2019s bathroom. Don\u2019t believe us? Check them out yourself, and for any extra assistance, you can always <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">reach out<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to us!<\/span><\/p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Luxurious Modular Interior Design Ideas